before the performance starts.

16
00:02:46,730 --> 00:02:48,750
Make yourself feel relaxed.

17
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:51,430
I'll watch your performance outside.

18
00:02:52,790 --> 00:02:53,700
P'Thanu.

19
00:02:55,390 --> 00:02:55,960
Yes?

20
00:02:57,780 --> 00:03:00,110
Can you keep me company until
my performance starts?

21
00:05:18,870 --> 00:05:21,230
[I won't care no matter
who approaches me.]

22
00:05:22,990 --> 00:05:24,270
[It's because this bow]

23
00:05:25,840 --> 00:05:27,280
[is the only thing
I care about right now.]

24
00:05:27,760 --> 00:05:28,590
[That's all.]

25
00:06:23,430 --> 00:06:25,700
And, don't forget to thank your friend.

26
00:06:25,700 --> 00:06:27,510
He reported the incident to the school.

27
00:06:27,670 --> 00:06:29,010
If he didn't do so,

28
00:06:29,010 --> 00:06:31,260
the wrongdoer wouldn't have been
punished in the first place.

29
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:34,350
Tong.

30
00:06:35,330 --> 00:06:36,950
I need to tell you something.

31
00:07:04,230 --> 00:07:07,320
Pok? What are you doing here?

32
00:07:09,890 --> 00:07:10,980
Have you seen Tong?

33
00:07:11,340 --> 00:07:12,660
I need to speak to him.

34
00:07:14,330 --> 00:07:15,800
He went to take a break.

35
00:07:17,080 --> 00:07:19,000
If he's back,

36
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:20,460
please tell him

37
00:07:20,710 --> 00:07:22,550
to stay here after the performance.

38
00:07:22,550 --> 00:07:24,460
